videos.description: Tyler Herro steps back and drains the 3-pointer over the outstretched arms of Anthony Davis.
videos.headline: Herro drains 3 over AD

videos.description: LeBron James drops the pass to Dwight Howard who flushes it with two hands and gets the foul.

videos.headline: LeBron finds Howard for the and-1 dunk

videos.description: LeBron James dribbles up and finds himself wide-open for the easy 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron left wide open for the 3) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron left wide open for the 3

videos.description: LeBron James finds the soft spot in the zone and throws the bounce pass to Anthony Davis for the easy dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron drops dime to AD for the slam) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron drops dime to AD for the slam

videos.description: LeBron James goes strong to the basket and finishes the layup plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron goes right through Iguodala for the and-1) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron goes right through Iguodala for the and-1

videos.description: Alex Caruso finds himself open for the 3, and he knocks it down.
videos.headline: Caruso cans the 3

videos.description: Jimmy Butler finds a cutting Jae Crowder who muscles it in through Markieff Morris.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Crowder muscles in the layup) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crowder muscles in the layup

videos.description: Rajon Rondo throws the lob to LeBron James for the and-1 layup, then on the next possession he goes up to to AD for the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Rondo throws back-to-back lobs to LeBron and AD) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rondo throws back-to-back lobs to LeBron and AD

videos.description: Anthony Davis comes out of halftime emphatically knocking down three straight jumpers then gets the tough finish at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD comes out cookin, scores on 4 straight possessions to start 3rd quarter) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD comes out cookin, scores on 4 straight possessions to start 3rd quarter

videos.description: Anthony Davis is able to maneuver his body and finish the tough tip in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Davis contorts his body for tough tip in) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis contorts his body for tough tip in

videos.description: Udonis Haslem tries to motivate his teammates during a third-quarter timeout.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Misc. (Haslem tries to fire up Heat during timeout) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haslem tries to fire up Heat during timeout

videos.description: Kendrick Nunn is able to finish the layup as LeBron James tries to get the chasedown block.

videos.headline: Nunn beats the chasing LeBron to the rim for the layup

videos.description: Anthony Davis thinks he has an easy layup but he is rejected by Kendrick Nunn at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Nunn meets Davis at the rim for the denial) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nunn meets Davis at the rim for the denial

videos.description: Alex Caruso finds a cutting Anthony Davis who emphatically throws it down with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Davis seals game with huge jam) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis seals game with huge jam

videos.description: LeBron James breaks down the Lakers Game 2 win in the NBA Finals and how they can get better going forward in the series.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (LeBron knows AD will come through every night) 2020/10/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron knows AD will come through every night

videos.description: Tim Legler breaks down how Anthony Davis was able to dominate Miami's zone defense.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (How AD took advantage of a Bam-less Heat) 2020/10/2 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: How AD took advantage of a Bam-less Heat

videos.description: Rajon Rondo gives credit to the Lakers' leadership for the team's success and notes the Kobe-like mindset the team has developed will be key in putting the Heat away in the Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Rondo believes Kobe-like mentality has been key in Lakers' success) 2020/10/02 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Rondo believes Kobe-like mentality has been key in Lakers' success

videos.description: Jimmy Butler explains that the Heat miss Bam Adebayo's presence, but they have to take caution and not make his injury worse by bringing him back too soon.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Butler: Heat being careful to not bring Bam back too soon) 2020/10/2

videos.headline: Butler: Heat being careful not to bring Bam back too soon

videos.description: Frank Vogel speaks to how special Anthony Davis is to the Lakers, calling him a "unicorn" and explaining how strong Davis' resolve is to win an NBA title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Vogel impressed by Davis' will to win a title) 2020/10/3

videos.headline: Vogel impressed by Davis' will to win a title
